headline: Jacobs Increases Quarterly Dividend
summary: The Board of Directors of Jacobs (NYSE:J) has declared a quarterly cash dividend payable to shareholders in the amount of $0.32 per share of Jacobs common stock, an increase of 10% from its previous quarterly dividend of $0.29. This dividend will be paid on March 21, 2025, to shareholders of record as of the close of business on Feb. 21, 2025.

headline: Jacobs Selected to Operate and Maintain Jackson, Mississippi, Water Treatment System
summary: Jacobs (NYSE:J) was selected to operate and maintain the water treatment system in Jackson, Mississippi, by JXN Water, the entity responsible for ensuring reliable water service for citizens in the state's largest city. This contract follows a short-term operations and maintenance (O&M) agreement that provided nearly 180,000 residents in and around Jackson with more reliable drinking water.
